{"tid":122502,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印度火箭連放104粒人造衞星創世界紀錄","createTime":"2017-02-16T05:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T09:57:21.000Z","uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01e79941f07e083552c217f6daa6d2164f1b5273","tid":122502,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:30:15.000Z","msg":"火箭在當地早上9時28分升空，時速2.7萬公里，於30分鐘內放出所有人造衞星。這些衞星分別來自包括印度、美國、以色列、哈薩克及瑞士等國，最大一枚重714公斤，用作觀察地球狀況，另外103枚合共重664公斤。俄羅斯於2014年在同一次任務中發射39個衞星，今次的數量大幅超越舊紀錄。印度總理莫迪在Twitter表示：「這個卓越的壯舉&hellip;&hellip;是太空科學界和我們國家的另一個驕傲時刻。」<br />\n<br />\n印度近年銳意發展太空科技。負責今次任務的極軌衞星運載火箭（PSLV）是印度自家製作，ISRO亦正致力研究送太空人到太空，以及在未來探索木星和金星。相對美國太空總署（NASA）的研究項目，ISRO項目的成本低廉得多，據統計印度2013年的火星探測器發射計劃，只花了7,300萬美元（約5.7億港元），是美國同類計劃的一成多。<br />\n<br />\n美聯社/法新社/路透社  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170216/19929656\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170216%2F19929656&d=NKClBOrNcUwYLVyzdKWJdUbWhtBCnEJYRTWbVbFBOac%3D&h=0399d437\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Finternational%2Fart%2F20170216%2F19929656&h=e0f8ac97\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20170216/19929656</a>"},{"pid":"938d213803ae4009ddc36e3baaec2707213c35af","tid":122502,"uid":19353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:41:31.000Z","msg":"我幻想到個畫面好似係太空產卵咁 不停係碌野度噴野出野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"288994a9610bae6c11c402339956989ab575c942","tid":122502,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T05:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我幻想到個畫面好似係太空產卵咁 不停係碌野度噴野出野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9e97778adbb2923f9181b73de5727dbbef1bc6c","tid":122502,"uid":72725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit